data.description: Welcome to your dream home in a beautiful neighborhood! This elegant 2-story residence features five spacious bedrooms and four luxurious bathrooms. The open-concept living area seamlessly connects the living room, dining area, and gourmet kitchen, perfect for entertaining. Enjoy the tranquility of the primary suite with its own on-suite bathroom. The backyard offers a peaceful oasis for outdoor gatherings. Conveniently located near amenities, recreational facilities, and excellent schools. Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a five bedroom, four bathroom home in a beautiful neighborhood. Schedule your showing today!
